      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bonds-fall-as-traders-pounce-on-fragile-return-of-risk-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着本周早些时候席卷全球市场的恐慌情绪逐渐消退，美国和欧洲政府债券价格下跌。]]></description>
